M||Use |Composer for layout/composition, Logic nodes for automation and branching, br nodes for identity consistency, Lipsync/Subtitles for vd character work, or Integration nodes for distribution. Load this skill when the us's pm involves ad, localization, A/B testing, QA checkpoints, multi-step text processing, or publishing to external platforms.
