M|When|it|You're building **ad creatives** that combine multiple elements
M|When|it|You need **text processing / pm engineering** in the workflow
M|When|it|You want **localization or A/B variants** w/o manual rebuilding
M|When|it|You need **QA checkpoints** before publishing
M|When|it|You want to **animate characters** or add **speech to images**
M|When|it|You're **distributing outputs** to sl/ad platforms
