M|Huma|**Us|** Any production pipeline where qual matters before output is published.
M|Huma|Inse|
M|Huma|tx|```
M|Huma|tx|GenerateImage → HumanReview → Composer → MetaAds
M|Huma|tx|```
M|Huma|tx|The workflow pauses, a human approves or rejects the asset, then execution continues.
M|Rout|**Us|** Send one node's output to multiple downstream nodes w/o duplicating or re-running.
M|Rout|tx|```
M|Rout|tx|GenerateImage → Router → RemoveBackground
M|Rout|→ Ch|1 for Instagram)
M|Rout|→ Ch|16 for TikTok)
M|Rout|tx|→ UpscaleImage
M|Rout|tx|```
M|Rout|tx|The im is generated once; Router distributes it to all four paths.
M|Rena|**Us|** Organized file naming, esp before Google Drive export.
M|Rena|tx|```
